lender.name: Chris
lender.loan_because: I feel very fortunate to live in a community that offers up help to others unquestioned. I love seeing how even a little help can go a long way.

lender.name: Kelsey
lender.loan_because: It's the right thing to do.

lender.name: Luke
lender.loan_because:
empowering people is cool. This is a great way to help someone change their life and the lives of others in their community. It is interesting, fun, and free!
Give a person a fish and you feed them for a day. Teach a person to fish and you feed them for a lifetime.

lender.name: Ashley
lender.loan_because: I have always been interested in helping others and I saw KIVA as a great opportunity to do so. I am in the process of achieving my goal of becoming a therapist, and I would love to do what I can to help others achieve their goals as well.

lender.name: Lisa
lender.loan_because: it is a nice thing to do (and also because of Nerdfrighters.)
lender.occupational_info: I work in a Library/Archive. My job right now is to move collections around.

lender.name: Chip
lender.loan_because: It is a good thing to do.

lender.name: Maggie
lender.loan_because: I think it is a kind thing to do and I want to help people instead of just sitting around doing nothing about issues.

lender.name: Janelle
lender.loan_because: it is a personal way to give back. I can see the people I'm helping and know their stories. I also lend because if I was in their situation, I'd hope that someone would help me.

lender.name: Blake
lender.loan_because: my donations may be small, but my hopes for others to achieve their dreams is great.

lender.name: Bennett
lender.loan_because: I am a Christian who serves a God of second chances, and I believe I should give others some help too.
